description: B Sweet Catering's new dessert truck! Serving freshly baked cupcakes, pies, cookies, breads, & other sweets. Voted best desserts in LA! Powered by @mybsweetWelcome to B Sweet! If you are looking to bring back the taste of homemade desserts like Grandma used to make, then B Sweet is the place. We are a local based company in Los Angeles and are dedicated to delivering the finest quality baked goods. This young company has captured the loyal following of those who appreciate the old fashioned homemade goodness. So if you want to treat yourself to something decadent, delicious and extraordinary, look no further. Its "One- of- a- kind baked goods made fresh daily" is ideal for all your delicious baked goods needs.
